      ('f1 * 'f2 * 'f3 * 'f4 * 'f5 * 'f6 * 'f7 * 'f8 * 'f9 * 'f10) encoding

    (** Create a larger object from the encodings of two smaller ones.
      @raise Invalid_argument if both arguments are not objects  or if both
